{"title": "Akční hrdina", "content": "<div><span style=\"color:#fff;background-color:#000\"><em><span style=\"text-align:center\">Slova jsou slova a mladost je mladost,</span></em></span><br style=\"color:#27292b;text-align:center\"><span style=\"color:#fff;background-color:#000\"><em><span style=\"text-align:center\">genitálie si přejí svou radost.</span></em></span><br style=\"color:#27292b;text-align:center\"><span style=\"color:#fff;background-color:#000\"><em><span style=\"text-align:center\">Trochu se vraždilo, trochu se kradlo,</span></em></span><br style=\"color:#27292b;text-align:center\"><span style=\"color:#fff;background-color:#000\"><em><span style=\"text-align:center\">pereme, pereme špinavé prádlo.</span></em></span></div>", "published": "2017-07-03T21:21:00Z", "tags": [], "filename": "/2017/07/akcni-hrdina.html"}